name: Rohan Tarang, Wakad
addressl1: Near Hinjewadi Bridge
details: When you open a window of a Rohan Tarang apartment, you open to neatly landscaped gardens or a panoramic view of the entire city skyline. This is because the layout has been planned in such a way that the windows don’t open on other windows. And every time you open the door, your home will not be on display for the world to see. Each doorway is planned in a way such that it opens into a lobby instead of your living room. Run in screaming if you wish and yet you won’t be disturbing a soul. This is because there are no common walls between homes. So no irritating knocking noises from the other side, or noise creeping in from the other side.
